channel.title: Server wont stay on my computer?
channel.description: I'm trying to download a source. Everytime I download it, it goes to my desktop and then it gets deleted. I tried saving the .rar and extracting it manually instead of having it automatically do it. It just deletes the .rar off of my desktop too? I thought it was my av, microsoft sercurity essentials, deleting them on its own since it thinks theres a virus in it. But ive downloaded this source multiple times and never had my av automatically delete it. So i dont think it is my av deleting it. But then what is?
